  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Season the lamb shoulder with salt, black pepper, ground cumin, and smoked paprika.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together chopped fenugreek leaves, minced garlic, and lemon juice.",
    "Brush the grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder to the grill and cook for 4 minutes per side.",
    "Transfer the lamb to a cutting board and let rest for 10 minutes.",
    "In the same grill, add the sliced roasted red bell pepper and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Slice the lamb shoulder into thick strips and serve with fenugreek-garlic sauce, red bell pepper, and chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
